{"tid":220893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殲英犬風波】恒大球迷會劃清界線 得罪玻璃心網軍","createTime":"2017-04-28T09:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T10:47:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8467309e5c738a4b608c085296db5c6c5860eacb","tid":220893,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170428/large/1493360634_d7d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170428%2Flarge%2F1493360634_d7d2.jpg&h=992e285b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣州恒大喺周二亞洲聯賽冠軍盃G組分組賽作客6:0擊敗港超球隊東方龍獅場波，因有坐喺旺角場作客球迷區嘅粉絲喺比賽末段展示「殲英犬 滅港毒」嘅標語為時數十秒，令球隊周四被亞洲足協（AFC）起訴，涉嫌違反AFC紀律和道德守則，面臨閉門作賽同罰款等處分。廣州20個球迷協會周五就發表聯合聲明，同4位舉起橫額嘅球迷劃清界線，指4人並非球迷會註冊會員，對佢哋嘅身份、行動並不知情，又表示多年來跟隨球隊文明、理性觀賽，從未出現過違規橫額：「我們熱愛足球，喜歡足球，享受足球帶來的興趣，不想也不會涉及政治，更不想被別有用心的人抹黑廣州球迷的形象、破壞廣州香港兩地球迷的感情。現得知，非廣州球迷的行為可能導致亞洲足協會對我們深愛的球隊進行處罰。在此，我們懇切希望亞洲足協能對事件展開深入調查，秉公執法，不要敷衍了事，草率決定，不要傷害廣大中國球迷的感情。」<br />\n<br />\n本來呢段聲明「情理兼備」，從劃清界線以至免除懲罰角度嚟睇可能有啲幫助，最弊係一眾愛國網軍、憤青梗係唔收貨，紛紛喺相關新聞留言話呢班球迷「不要臉」、「不配當恒大球迷，也不配當個中國人」、「作為內地人竟然不幫自己人，還想認香港老爹？」云云，仲應該聲明「球迷協會熱愛祖國，堅決反對一切分裂祖國的行為」&hellip;&hellip;就連俾AFC調查中嘅恒大一樣捱鬧，話大是大非面前點解球會唔抗辯！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56625502&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56625502%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170428&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=46539e5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56625502%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170428&h=94a47b51\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56625502&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170428</a>"},{"pid":"05608a7da803fc6eb7316e34b655ebbf4d239b13","tid":220893,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:14:28.000Z","msg":"同中國人談團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae91435beb81c9bd7d18f83c3a810b3198f8d2c0","tid":220893,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"拉banner果幾條友慘變condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6599f7da4462b45157638da09b743075e16b024","tid":220893,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08058dcb4d16184b860d92985a0868bb759a28e","tid":220893,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"除左涉事四人,可見恆大球迷毫無悔意,理應直接取消資格"},{"pid":"b976aa5de02df04e1e20681f18911c7890fab93d","tid":220893,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左涉事四人,可見恆大球迷毫無悔意,理應直接取消資格</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bfa8ad0ba8b428c20ab2d6321ae9cb50420b81","tid":220893,"uid":38441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"我都話大陸直接解散足球，杯葛足球啦"},{"pid":"70bcab42f744299f4a5b2f52350c561b71f7922a","tid":220893,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都話大陸直接解散足球，杯葛足球啦</blockquote><br />\n集體自盡 杯葛全世界比較好"}]}